channel.title: Looking for another 317 pi developer the server is already up online vps hosted
channel.description:
Hey guys I am looking for another 317 pi developer because right now I am the only programmer and could do with some help the server is up online vps hosted. If selected you need to be dedicated, motivated, and active, you'll also have tasks set that we expect to be completed without any bugs/leaks. if you wish to join the development then please apply now:
Name: best way of contact: experience: proof: how many servers have you worked on?:
the person selected or person's selected will be given development rank in the game and other bonuses if good enough we will even start to talk about maybe giving you a "wage" at end of each month for the hard work. Only serious people apply please
